Package: wnvSurv
Title: West Nile Virus Surveillance Functions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Toby", "Koch", , "r.tobiaskoch@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shared functions for West Nile virus mosquito surveillance work
    in the Ebel Lab. Consolidates data ingest, cleaning, abundance/pooled
    infection rate/vector index calculations, and standard plots used across
    the wnv-ss_trap_hx_combiner and wnv-ss-wkly_report pipelines.
